1. install node.js for your platform

2. install required packages

    npm i

3. create a config.json file for your server, like this,

{
  "user":"username",
  "password":"XXXXXX",
  "server":"https://joe64.dev.cpanel.net:2087",
  "page":"/scripts/command?PFILE=Security_Center"
}

leave page as "" if you intend to test the homepage

4. download chromedriver from 

    http://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/index.html

put the downloaded chromedriver in your $PATH, and make sure it is executable

5. run the tests

    node axe-test.js

6. please contact joe.zhou@cpanel.net if you spot a bug
